      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "The torrent needs updating, for sure.  We do not typically bother with updating the checkpoints in lock step with the torrent.\n\n_Ideally_, checkpoints are an evil hack that we want to go away.  Practically speaking, they save users a lot of CPU on initial sync.\n",
